{"tid":1742471,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"翻睇一套舊電影....好似睇香港預言咁","createTime":"2019-11-20T21:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T21:58:07.000Z","uid":275912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e48153820c90bb7030e498708a619e0bfa52457d","tid":1742471,"uid":275912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:29:43.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">果套電影就係阿凡達<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港有好大既利益</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">納美人既居住地下面有好值錢既礦石</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">被清洗，被統治</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">被屠殺</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一步一步侵蝕，不斷立惡法</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">用推土機清除聲音樹</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">示威，抗爭</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">反擊，消滅入侵者</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警話止暴制亂</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">上校話以暴制暴</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">18區開花</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">15族合力反抗</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">200萬人示威</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">2萬戰士</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">彈珠對自動步槍</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">弓箭對飛機大炮</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">下面既仲會唔會發生？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">自然界既反撲，無限兵力支援<br />\n將地球人趕出潘朵拉星</span></div>"},{"pid":"54a69e0e485cc351ea9b27f48c901afaba0f26df","tid":1742471,"uid":135995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:58:07.000Z","msg":"好浪漫 個現實係好多族都死晒"}]}